            Articles</heading><section id="ID_1438412097123_060" name="s1" temporalId="sch2_s1" class="no_header"><num value="1">1.</num><content>Any coin which is, or was formerly, current coin of Hong Kong or elsewhere.
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2000/65">65 of 2000 s.
                    3</ref>)</sourceNote><marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412097123_068" name="s2" temporalId="sch2_s2" class="no_header"><num value="2">2.</num><content>Any article which has been used, or is intended to be used, for medical, dental, veterinary, scientific or industrial use.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412097123_076" name="s3" temporalId="sch2_s3" class="no_header"><num value="3">3.</num><content>Any article of platinum thread.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412097139_004" name="s4" temporalId="sch2_s4" class="no_header"><num value="4">4.</num><content>Any raw material (including any bar, plate, sheet, foil, wire, strip or tube) or bullion.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412097139_012" name="s5" temporalId="sch2_s5" class="no_header"><num value="5">5.</num><content>Any article or part of an article which is so small or thin as to render the marking of it impracticable, and which is less than 2 grams in weight.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412097139_020" name="s6" temporalId="sch2_s6" class="no_header"><num value="6">6.</num><content>Any article manufactured more than 100 years ago, provided that this is so stated in the invoice or receipt required by <ref>paragraph 6(1)</ref>.</content></section></schedule><schedule id="ID_1438403065990_002" name="sch3" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="sch3"><num value="3">Schedule 3</num><note class="align_right" role="crossReferences" type="inline">[<ref href="/hk/cap362C/s7">para.
